HEADWORD: Rutylene
<hw>Ru"ty*lene</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A liquid hydrocarbon, <chform>C10H18</chform>, of the acetylene
series. It is produced artificially.</def>⟦br⟧
